objects.name: CVE-2025-42974
objects.description:
Remote exploitation of a design error vulnerability in SAP's NetWeaver AS ABAP and ABAP Platform could allow an attacker to bypass authorization techniques on the targeted host.

A design error vulnerability has been identified in NetWeaver AS ABAP and ABAP Platform.

Further details are not available at the time of this writing. ACI will update this report as more details become available.
